# Unicode.GeneralCategory.mathSymbol

**Case**

A symbol of mathematical use.

## Declaration

```swift
case mathSymbol
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Math_Symbol` (abbreviated `Sm`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
